.Fc
.fi
.nf
.Ft int
.Fo libexe_check_file_signature
.Fa "const char *filename"
.Fa "libexe_error_t **error"
.Fc
.fi
.Pp
Available when compiled with wide character string support:
.nf
.Ft int
.Fo libexe_check_file_signature_wide
